MAX grounding, net of insurance recoveries. Additionally, we recorded a charge of $109 related to ongoing litigation
associated with recoverable costs on U.S. government contracts. During the second quarter of 2018, we recorded a
charge of $148 related to the outcome of the Spirit litigation and a reach-forward loss on KC-46A Tanker of $426.
